{
  "stem": "22728.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was either very early in '39 or very late in '38, around that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh my goodness.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All my little aunts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- I call them the little aunts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were a little diminutive women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came to tea a lot, and I loved them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were very delicate ladies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were four of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were picked up and taken away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was my favorite aunt-- my father's aunt, really, my great aunt-- who would make-- the moment she heard our voices, she would fix something wonderful to eat.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then there was another one in Cologne that used to come and visit and stay with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was gone in no time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyone who couldn't really defend themself very well disappeared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think anyone around us knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The gentile's didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can honestly say that I don't think people knew a lot around us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did we know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, there was an underground, and it became very frightening, very frightening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father, still, until then, was so optimistic and so sure that this is impossible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It can't last.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the outside world would intervene.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Americans will come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was incredible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, how do you find out?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By people whispering to each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You never said these things on the telephone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Never, never, never.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Telephone wasn't safe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well they told us that there were camps that were probably-- where people died from malnutrition or, or-- and then we heard rumors about pogroms in Poland.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we weren't very far away from Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Hitler marched into Poland after we left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we heard all kinds of rumors all along.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was enough to make your hair stand on edge.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
